Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory39.jpg'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryFireLiziNew.prefab', 2: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "I can't take these guards down... fast enough...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "Commandant! I can't last much longer if this continues... You have to run for the opening I create as soon as the alarm on my frame pings!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'I will fight to my last breath to make sure you can get out!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'There has to be another way!', 3: '9', 4: "I won't leave you behind, Lucia!", 5: '9'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "I've made my decision! I'll push you away myself if I have to when the time comes!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Iron Maiden', 3: 'Stop your attack, my servants!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Iron Maiden', 3: 'The Queen has extended her invitation into her chamber to this human... Servants! Bring me that human!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "You're not taking Commandant away!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Iron Maiden', 3: 'Servants, I said bring me...', 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryLouDianNew.prefab', 3: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "You said you're a royal guard, but I don't see any difference between you and those servants of yours...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "(His frame is heavily damaged) I received Commandant's request for assistance by the time I climbed out from underground... I must prioritize Commandant's safety...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'What have you done to yourself?!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'The guards tried to keep me inside a tunnel, so I collapsed it... and here I am.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "(Points his gun toward the Iron Maiden) I've crossed paths with her before... She bolted halfway through... It seems like her target is the commandant.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "You're right. She was very unambiguous about that.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryLouDianNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "If that Queen of yours wants to see Commandant, you'll have to go through us first.", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Iron Maiden', 3: "You dare defy Her Majesty's will?! Constructs, you don't even deserve to be servants!", 4: '2'}
